{"tid":1911480,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"E'Dawn向前線致敬　泫雅手寫信為中韓粉絲打氣","createTime":"2020-03-05T10:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T11:23:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0409c4d4a05364e94e9ebba9b611288a2c7747b5","tid":1911480,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:54:39.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情在全球漫延，韓國性感女歌手泫雅今早在Instagram上載親自公開韓文手寫信，提醒大家要注意健康，希望大家能一起克服難關。<br />\n<br />\n她今午亦在微博上載簡體中文字版本的手寫信，為中國粉絲打氣：「各位，好久不見，大家都過得好嗎？希望大家都可以戰勝疫情！所有的朋友們照顧好身體，我們一起加油！武漢加油！中國加油！」<br />\n<br />\n男友E'Dawn今日亦公開畫有韓國國旗及醫務人員的畫作，並寫上：「謝謝你們，向你們致敬，我愛你們。」<br />\n<br />\n而女星高雅娜今日亦上載拿着手寫字條的照片，為前線醫護人員打氣：「真心感謝在最前線努力的你們，希望正在經歷困難的人都可以早日康復，我們一起加油吧，加油吧大韓民國！」"},{"pid":"b9a6dda4ef5951744fd624fb8f32acbd899fa18c","tid":1911480,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200305/photo/bkn-20200305165022096-0305_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200305165029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200305165022096-0305_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200305165029&h=6df23124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff075310d15d4e9393d2154a46264ffa73f3ab5a","tid":1911480,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200305/photo/bkn-20200305165022096-0305_00862_001_04b.jpg?20200305165029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200305165022096-0